data.description: Come enjoy the peaceful setting and sweeping views at this single level West Valley home. There is ample parking as well as space for your RV and an oversized two car garage.  The backyard backs up to open space and sweeping views of the Flathead Valley and Glacier National Park. The deck, firepit, and hot tub offer the perfect place to enjoy the views or to entertain. Inside, an open floor plan with a large living room and wood burning stove make for a relaxing environment on cool winter nights. The primary bedroom boasts two walk in closets and a spacious bathroom. Each of the three remaining bedrooms have their own walk in closets which provide abundant storage. The property has VRBO potential. Call Carrie Fennessy at 406-314-3099 or your real estate professional.
